org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview
Class AeJsTreeBuilder

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.web.processview.AeJsTreeBuilder
public class AeJsTreeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object

This class generates the Java Script needed to display a Tree View control. Specifically, the tree view used is the LGPLed NanoTree (http://nanotree.sourceforge.net/).
